modules.description: This module implements glob pattern parsing and matching operations, supporting creation of glob expressions from strings, testing strings against globs, and handling common glob patterns like universal or empty matches. It works with string-based file paths and filename extensions, enabling filtering or matching operations during build configuration. Concrete use cases include selecting files by extension, checking path inclusion against glob patterns, and converting glob expressions to and from string representations.

Implements glob pattern parsing and matching operations, including creating glob expressions from strings, testing strings against globs, and handling universal or empty matches. Works with string-based file paths and filename extensions to support filtering during build configuration. Used for selecting files by extension, checking path inclusion, and converting glob expressions to and from string representations.
